1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:07,017
We have come a long way, Kuku, from very humble beginnings.

2
00:00:07,024 --> 00:00:14,021
And we learned valuable lessons which will help us grow our new economy.

3
00:00:21,014 --> 00:00:28,021
Who could have imagined the impact that the discovery of oil would have on us?

4
00:00:31,019 --> 00:00:41,004
Oil brought in a new era of wealth and prosperity to Abu Lumba

5
00:00:41,005 --> 00:00:47,002
With our new wealth, we transformed a barren desert town into a shining modern oasis!

6
00:00:49,004 --> 00:00:59,016
Those were truly The Golden Years...
